OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has called for
OL,8,Funrestricted transit in the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz after Donald Trump said he
OL,10,Fwould levy a 20% toll on shipping for
OL,11,Fsafe passage through the critical
OL,12,Fwaterway.
OL,14,FThe outgoing British Prime Minister
OL,15,Falso urged an end to the fighting and
OL,16,Fa return to the negotiating table as
OL,17,Fthe US launched the third consecutive
OL,18,Fnight of strikes against Iran over the
OL,19,Fcontested strategic sea route.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FSir Keir made his remarks after the
OL,8,FAmerican president claimed charging a
OL,9,Ffee on cargo for use of the Gulf
OL,10,Fchannel was a "matter of fairness" to
OL,11,Fcover the cost of providing security.
OL,13,FThe move has sparked a backlash in the
OL,14,FUK, with the Liberal Democrats
OL,15,Fbranding it "state-backed highway
OL,16,Frobbery", "an act of economic
OL,17,Fextortion" and "a flagrant violation
OL,18,Fof international law".
OL,26,@rD@OOUrD@bO]wD@MOUxD@HO]xD@KOUyD@JO]yD@
OL,26,APOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FSenior White House figures have
OL,8,Frepeatedly voiced their opposition to
OL,9,Ftolls being imposed by Iran.
OL,11,FThe vital sea route had been open
OL,12,Fbefore the conflict launched by the US
OL,13,Fand Israel on February 28.
OL,15,FMr Trump also announced a blockade of
OL,16,FIranian ports would resume, having
OL,17,Fbeen lifted last month as part of the
OL,18,Finterim ceasefire deal he has declared
OL,19,Fover following renewed hostilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
