FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FThe US military said it will come back
OL,8,Finto force on July 14 at 9pm UK time.
OL,10,FThe president later announced he would
OL,11,Fbe making an address to the nation on
OL,12,FThursday evening, but gave no further
OL,13,Fdetails.
OL,15,FHe also described the Tehran regime as
OL,16,F"sleazebags".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
