FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FThe action by the White House comes
OL,8,Famid an escalating struggle between
OL,9,FWashington and Tehran over the strait,
OL,10,Fwhich has seen both sides exchange
OL,11,Ffire.
OL,13,FThe latest clash came after Iran
OL,14,Fattacked a container ship on Sunday in
OL,15,Fthe strait.
OL,17,FIran claims it controls the waterway,
OL,18,Fwhile this is disputed by the US and
OL,19,Fother countries, which cite
OL,20,Finternational law on freedom of
OL,21,Fnavigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FWriting on his Truth Social platform,
OL,8,FMr Trump said: "The Hormuz Strait is
OL,9,FOPEN, and will remain OPEN, with or
OL,10,Fwithout Iran.
OL,12,F"We are reinstating the THE IRANIAN
OL,13,FBLOCKADE, so named because it is only
OL,14,Fstopping Iran's ships or customers
OL,15,Ffrom entering or leaving.
OL,17,F"All other countries will have fair
OL,18,Fand open use of the Strait."
OL,26,@pD@POUtD@AOUyD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FHe added: "The USA will be, from this
OL,8,Fpoint forward, known as 'THE GUARDIAN
OL,9,FOF THE HORMUZ STRAIT', but as such,
OL,10,Fand as a matter of FAIRNESS, will be
OL,11,Freimbursed, at the rate of 20% on all
OL,12,Fcargo shipped, for any and all costs
OL,13,Fnecessary to do the job of providing
OL,14,Fsafety and security to this very
OL,15,Fvolatile section of the World.
OL,17,F"The process and formation will begin
OL,18,Fimmediately."
OL,26,@oD@KOUyD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FLater, speaking at an event at the
OL,8,FWhite House, Mr Trump said: "I want to
OL,9,Fbe reimbursed because we're protecting
OL,10,Fa very rich portion of the world,
OL,11,Fwe're spending money."
OL,13,FBut speaking at a meeting in Paris
OL,14,Fduring his final days in office, Sir
OL,15,FKeir said: "These attacks must stop.
OL,17,F"We urgently need to see a resumption
OL,18,Fof the ceasefire and negotiations on
OL,19,Fthe remaining issues, alongside
OL,20,Funrestricted freedom of navigation in
OL,21,Fthe straits.
OL,26,@pD@]OUsD@VO]wD@LOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,F"We are united in support of this
OL,8,Fprocess. And we are ready to deploy
OL,9,Fassets to help get ships moving again."
OL,11,FLiberal Democrat foreign affairs
OL,12,Fspokesman Calum Miller MP said:
OL,13,F"Donald Trump's plan to slap a 20% tax
OL,14,Fon shipping through the Strait of
OL,15,FHormuz is nothing short of state-
OL,16,Fbacked highway robbery. Ambushing
OL,17,Fglobal trade at one of the world's
OL,18,Fmost vital chokepoints is an act of
OL,19,Feconomic extortion.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@gO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,F"Extracting tolls like this is a
OL,8,Fflagrant violation of international
OL,9,Flaw.
OL,11,F"The UK Government cannot afford to be
OL,12,Fa passive bystander while a volatile
OL,13,FWhite House tears up the rules of
OL,14,Fglobal trade and regional stability,
OL,15,For while the Iranian regime continues
OL,16,Fto attack vessels in the Strait.
OL,18,F"Both Donald Trump and Tehran are once
OL,19,Fagain holding the global economy to
OL,20,Fransom.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,F"Keir Starmer must immediately co-
OL,8,Fordinate with our international allies
OL,9,Fto reject this lawless toll, protect
OL,10,Ffreedom of navigation, and work
OL,11,Furgently to de-escalate this rapidly
OL,12,Fexpanding conflict."
OL,14,FThe International Maritime
OL,15,FOrganisation, the United Nations
OL,16,Fagency which oversees safety and
OL,17,Fsecurity in international shipping,
OL,18,Fsaid: "There is no legal basis through
OL,19,Fwhich to introduce mandatory tolls
OL,20,Fsimply to transit through a strait."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@TO]zD@GOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
