OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FOnly last month, US secretary of state
OL,8,FMarco Rubio stressed the US was
OL,9,Fagainst Iran charging fees for ships
OL,10,Fto use the international waterway.
OL,12,FMr Trump recently joined other world
OL,13,Fleaders at the G7 summit in France,
OL,14,Fincluding Sir Keir, to confirm that
OL,15,F"the right of transit passage without
OL,16,Frestrictions or tolls is the bedrock
OL,17,Fof international trade".
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
