OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FMeanwhile, US central command
OL,8,F(Centcom), which oversees US military
OL,9,Foperations in the Middle East,
OL,10,Frevealed it had used one-way
OL,11,F"kamikaze" surface drones for the
OL,12,Ffirst time in its latest attacks on
OL,13,FIran to strike a submarine and ship
OL,14,Fmaintenance facility.
OL,16,FThe number of US military personnel to
OL,17,Fdie in the conflict currently stands
OL,18,Fat 14, with a total of 414 wounded.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FEnding Tehran's stranglehold on the
OL,8,Fsea route, which disrupted global oil
OL,9,Fand gas supplies and drove up fuel and
OL,10,Ffood prices, had been a key demand in
OL,11,Fprevious negotiations.
OL,13,FHowever, the initial deal reached
OL,14,Fbetween the US and Iran only provides
OL,15,Ffor safe, toll-free passage through
OL,16,Fthe waterway for 60 days, pending the
OL,17,Foutcome of a final agreement on
OL,18,FTehran's disputed nuclear plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784054883
OL,3,CStarmer calls for restriction-free
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as Trump threatens
OL,5,Ctolls
OL,7,FThe pact also leaves it to Iran and
OL,8,FOman, in conjunction with other Gulf
OL,9,Fstates, to "define the future
OL,10,Fadministration and maritime services
OL,11,Fin the Strait of Hormuz".
OL,13,FIran has continued to try to exert
OL,14,Fleverage over the channel, including
OL,15,Fdemanding ships seek permission to
OL,16,Ftransit and raising the spectre of
OL,17,Ffuture charges.
OL,26,@qD@LOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
